text: <s>[INST]What is NSC?[/INST] Nagarro Service Catalog is a web application that provides a single point of access to all the services that Nagarro offers to its employees. It is a self-service portal that allows employees to request for services, track the status of their requests, and provide feedback on the services they have received. It also provides a platform for Nagarro employees to share their ideas and suggestions for improving the services offered by Nagarro. </s>
